{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"67bbab0543","title":"一封信的纠纷","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"f85dd09a1a","index":0,"year":1957,"month":1,"day":3,"articleId":"67bbab0543"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"c8903b9ea6","name":"北京市"},{"id":"dd89ef9af3","name":"谢增辉"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"3734ff1e12","type":"title","text":"一封信的纠纷","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"67bbab0543"},{"id":"e0bd3dd9c0","type":"authors","text":"北京市谢增辉","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"67bbab0543"},{"id":"c91ea53818","type":"paragraph","text":"黄局长在电话室里，一眼扫见通讯员小张桌上放着一封用毛笔写的给中共中央××同志的挂号信。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"67bbab0543"},{"id":"76bbaf2aea","type":"paragraph","text":"“不忙发，我要同他谈一下！”","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"67bbab0543"},{"id":"5ac13381a5","type":"paragraph","text":"局长走出电话室，马上把老谢叫进他的办公室去。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"67bbab0543"},{"id":"1ba5dc2def","type":"paragraph","text":"“我们这个机构要变动了，你有什么意见吗？”","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"67bbab0543"},{"id":"1e893242ad","type":"paragraph","text":"“没什么意见。”","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"67bbab0543"},{"id":"2d505cbf31","type":"paragraph","text":"“没意见？”局长的神情和语气好象有点诧异，但仍然尽量克制自己的感情说：“你为什么向中央写信？”","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"67bbab0543"},{"id":"13328daf7b","type":"paragraph","text":"还没等老谢开腔，他又提出一连串的问题：“你跟××同志是什么关系？是亲戚吗？是朋友吗？是……”","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"67bbab0543"},{"id":"39ee1ed32c","type":"paragraph","text":"“没什么关系。”","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"67bbab0543"},{"id":"f1732b9732","type":"paragraph","text":"“没什么关系，你为什么要给他写信呢？”","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"67bbab0543"},{"id":"9a81746450","type":"paragraph","text":"“宪法上并没有规定普通公民不能跟中央的领导人写信吧。”","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"67bbab0543"},{"id":"1668cc4854","type":"paragraph","text":"局长沉默了一下，又断断续续地说：“嗯！……嗯！……反正，给中央写信要事先通过组织，通过领导，这是我们这儿的制度。你写信通过领导和组织吗？要知道，你这种作法不是在控告领导吗？”","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"67bbab0543"},{"id":"ecc9b745c5","type":"paragraph","text":"“我认为，以私人名义向中央写信并不是什么了不起的事情。”","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"67bbab0543"},{"id":"229741a9b6","type":"paragraph","text":"局长的火气好象又上来了，说道：“反正，你在我这个单位，你向中央写信就是控告我！”","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"67bbab0543"},{"id":"ef67689222","type":"paragraph","text":"“……。”","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"67bbab0543"},{"id":"6581b19f77","type":"paragraph","text":"他忽然想到说得有点过火，就转用劝告的口气说：“我希望你还是考虑考虑，那封信是发好，不发好。”","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"67bbab0543"},{"id":"997d74a40e","type":"paragraph","text":"谈话就到这里结束。信终究是发出去了。从此以后，老谢的各方面，特别是写信，黄局长都加倍地注意，不过他后来是否又发现了什么，就不知道了。","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"67bbab0543"},{"id":"be980f962f","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：1957年1月3日《人民日报》第8版。","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"67bbab0543"}],"page":{"id":"2c9660b976","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"67bbab0543","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}